name: Imprint - an ambient audiovisual étude in random key
description: A unique sequence of audiovisual études generated for every Hic et Nunc user. The seed phrase entered manually will produce a derived piece when you hit the "Play" button. To share a variation you like, copy the seed phrase and send it to a friend. Enjoy your unique audiovisual imprint on Hic et Nunc! System requirements: a desktop Chrome, Firefox or Edge browser.
